          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The total photoabsorption cross-section for 4He",
                " has been measured for the first time over a wide",
                " photon energy range (200 - 800 MeV). By using the",
                " large acceptance detector DAPHNE at the tagged",
                " photon facility of the MAMI microtron in Mianz",
                " high precision results with small systematic",
                " errors were obtained. This measurement shows that",
                " 4He has a behavior similar to heavy nuclei and,",
                " in particular, a reduction of the cross-section",
                " with respect to the lighter nuclei is found for",
                " Eg > 600 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
